Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.44,0:00:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.39,0:00:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了  就算是老鷹禿鷲你也不能輸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.20,0:00:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀小紗小姐  你這要求有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.58,0:00:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.40,0:00:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不會  只要努力就能成功
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.88,0:00:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勁啊  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.48,0:00:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多保重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.28,0:01:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天比往常更精神了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.41,0:01:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許它在寬闊的場所比較開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.18,0:01:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.26,0:01:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.14,0:01:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我幫你拿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.39,0:01:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.98,0:01:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來拿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.16,0:01:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.78,0:01:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我一不注意就馬上想接近美羽學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.34,0:01:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這蛆蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.83,0:01:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗凪？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.95,0:01:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別在意  這也算是社團成員的職責
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.25,0:01:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧  回去吧
